{"tid":1135623,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[又有新聞] 發文風波後首露面！Sana錄節目…台上哭了","createTime":"2019-05-02T12:08:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-02T16:39:34.000Z","uid":74065,"like":10,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f7a28e4d1cb67ce920d9eb355fff81a28ca532a1","tid":1135623,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T12:08:50.000Z","msg":"南韓女團「TWICE」的日籍成員Sana因4月30日在官方IG以日文發文，感嘆日本揮別平成年代，迎向令和，沒想到此舉卻引起大票南韓網友不滿，意外掀起罵戰。<br />\n<br />\nTWICE在Sana發文風波後，1日晚間首度現身音樂節目《Show Champion》，有在現場的粉絲事後在微博發文透露，Sana在節目預錄前，聽到台下的歌迷大喊「Sana加油」，她便在舞台上哭了出來，最後由成員扶下了台。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4066/4066616.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4066%2F4066616.jpg&h=b1c8e6b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲粉絲透露Sana哭了。（圖／翻攝自微博）<br />\n<br />\n而TWICE在音樂節目《Show Champion》的片段也流出，只見Sana站在子瑜、MOMO身後，全程低頭，一直沒有正面看鏡頭，神情更是顯露出憔悴，影片曝光後，讓粉絲心疼不已，「寶貝妳沒有做錯什麼呀！別不敢抬頭」、「看到她哭我也好傷心」、「躲在後面假裝堅強太讓人心疼了」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4066/4066617.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4066%2F4066617.jpg&h=7d62e62f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4066/4066618.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4066%2F4066618.jpg&h=a442f483&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲風波後首露面，Sana一直迴避鏡頭。（圖／翻攝自微博）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4066/4066619.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4066%2F4066619.jpg&h=68e8f41d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲網友留言。（圖／翻攝自微博）<br />\n►點我看影片！<br />\n<br />\n13億人都原諒左傻沙❤❤"},{"pid":"cadd65d02d8a415219a8814ff02b9830b738719c","tid":1135623,"uid":138138,"like":5,"dislike":23,"score":-18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T12:11:18.000Z","msg":"娜璉仲係全隊最靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"741e3c927813f9e928d77e9c7fee0e6e08f53e5b","tid":1135623,